<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.233.103096.figure57>
    dc:description "Figure 57. Uvariopsis congolana (De Wild.) Fries A leaves, lower side B trunk with long flowering pedicels C flower bud, side view D male flower, side view, note the long pedicel E detail of male flower, two petals removed, side view F stamen G female flower, top view, note the long pedicel H female flower, bottom view, note the two sepals I longitudinal section of female flower J carpel, front view and detail of ovules A, G from Halle 3039 B-F, H-J from Halle 2817. Drawings by Helene Lamourdedieu, from Le Thomas (1969; pl. 55, p. 305), Publications Scientifiques du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle, Paris." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/909916" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.233.103096.figure58>
    dc:description "Figure 58. Distribution map of Uvariopsis congolana. Shades of grey represent elevation, from white (sea level) to darker grey (higher elevation). The inset shows the extent of the map over Africa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/909917" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

